Morvern Callar;;2002;;R;;Drama;;6.8;;Lynne Ramsay;;Samantha Morton,Kathleen McDermott,Linda McGuire,Paul Popplewell,Ruby Milton,Dolly Wells,Dan Cadan,Carolyn Calder,Raife Patrick Burchell,Steve Cardwell,Bryan Dick,El Carrette,Andrew Flanagan,Des Hamilton,Mette Karlsvik,Andrew Knowles,Duncan McHardy,Mischa Richter;;Following her boyfriend's suicide, supermarket clerk Morvern Callar passes off his unpublished novel as her own. With the money her boyfriend left for his funeral, she leaves Scotland for Ibiza where she travels with her closest friend. The journey prompts a series of internal and external transformations for Morvern - ones which bring to light her experiences of grief, memory, freedom, and desire.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0300214/